UnitVaultManager::constructor
├── when any address param is zero
│   └── it reverts
└── when all params are valid
    ├── it sets LPUSD
    ├── it sets treasury
    └── it grants roles to governance


UnitVaultManager::depositAndMint
├── when contract is paused
│   └── it reverts
├── when deposit amount is zero
│   └── it reverts
├── when no adapter is registered
│   └── it reverts
├── when collateral is not active
│   └── it reverts
├── when mint amount is zero
│   └── it deposits collateral without minting
└── when mint amount is non zero
    ├── when no oracle is set
    │   └── it reverts
    ├── when mint would exceed LTV
    │   └── it reverts
    ├── when mint would exceed debt ceiling
    │   └── it reverts
    └── when all checks pass
        ├── it updates vault collateral and debt
        ├── it mints net LPUSD to the user
        ├── it mints fee to treasury
        └── it emits events


UnitVaultManager::repayAndWithdraw
├── when both amounts are zero
│   └── it reverts
├── when repay amount exceeds vault debt
│   └── it reverts
├── when withdrawal would make health factor below one
│   └── it reverts
├── when contract is paused
│   └── it does not revert
└── when all checks pass
    ├── it burns LPUSD from user
    ├── it reduces vault debt
    ├── it returns collateral to user
    └── it emits events


UnitVaultManager::healthFactor
├── when vault has no debt
│   └── it returns max uint256
└── when vault has debt
    └── it returns the correct scaled health factor


UnitVaultManager::setCollateralAdapter
├── when called by non-governance
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by governance
    ├── it sets the adapter
    └── it emits CollateralAdapterSet


UnitVaultManager::setRiskParams
├── when called by non-governance
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by governance
    ├── it updates risk params
    └── it emits RiskParamsSet


UnitVaultManager::setStabilityPool
├── when called by non-governance
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by governance
    ├── it sets the stability pool
    └── it emits StabilityPoolSet


UnitVaultManager::liquidateFromStabilityPool
├── when called by a non-stabilityPool
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by the stabilityPool
    ├── it burns LPUSD from the Stability Pool
    ├── it reduces vault debt and collateral
    ├── it reduces total debt
    └── it emits StabilityPoolLiquidation


UnitVaultManager::setLiquidationManager
├── when called by non-governance
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by governance
    ├── it sets the liquidation manager
    └── it emits LiquidationManagerSet


UnitVaultManager::liquidateExternal
├── when called by a non-liquidationManager
│   └── it reverts with VaultManager_OnlyLiquidationManager
├── when debtToRepay is zero
│   └── it reverts with VaultManager_ZeroAmount
├── when no adapter is registered
│   └── it reverts with VaultManager_NoAdapter
├── when debt exceeds vault debt
│   └── it reverts with VaultManager_InsufficientDebt
├── when total collateral out exceeds vault collateral
│   └── it reverts with VaultManager_InsufficientCollateral
└── when all checks pass
    ├── it burns LPUSD from the LiquidationManager
    ├── it reduces vault debt and total debt
    ├── it reduces vault collateral
    ├── it sends collateralToLiquidator to the liquidator
    ├── it sends collateralReturned to the vault owner
    ├── it skips the return transfer when collateralReturned is zero
    └── it emits ExternalLiquidation


UnitVaultManager::pause
├── when called by non-guardian
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by guardian
    └── it pauses the contract


UnitVaultManager::unpause
├── when called by non-guardian
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by guardian
    └── it unpauses the contract
